In Bamboo 2.0 we switched to using the cvs rlog command, in place of using cvs log command to get the changelists.

Unfortunately, this command is not supported by CVS servers 1.11.1 and below and was only implemented in 1.11.1p and perfoming a CVS rlog command returns the following errror -
{code}
cvs [rlog aborted]: server does not support rlog
{code}

